## Azure Configuration Review - Zero to Hero steps:
- AZ-900 training (10 hours) - 2 weeks, self-learning
  - learning material: udemy.com, acloudguru.com, Microsoft resources
- AZ-500 training (30-40 hours) - 2 months, self-learning
  - learning material: udemy.com, acloudguru.com, Microsoft resources
- PowerShell training (10 hours) - 2 weeks (optional but recommended), self-learning
  - learning material: udemy.com, other courses
- Shadowing 3-5 projects

## AWS Configuration Review - Zero to Hero steps:
- Amazon Cloud Practitioner (10 hours) - 2 weeks, self-learning
  - learning material: udemy.com, acloudguru.com, Amazon resources
  - https://deloittedevelopment.udemy.com/course/aws-certified-cloud-practitioner-new/learn/lecture/20053378#overview
  - https://deloittedevelopment.udemy.com/course/practice-exams-aws-certified-cloud-practitioner/learn/quiz/4915789#overview
- Amazon Cloud Solution Architect Associate - 2 months self-learning (can be exchanged to Cloud Developer or Cloud Administrator certificates)
  - learning material: udemy.com, acloudguru.com, amazon resources
- Amazon Cloud Security Associate (30-40 hours) - 2 months, self-learning
  - learning material: udemy.com, acloudguru.com, amazon resources
- Shadowing 3-5 projects
- Hands on learning of the following tools (2-4 hours) - on a project
  - Prowler
  - Scout2

## Advanced Trainings (not included in Zero to Hero)
- Pentester Academy Cloud Security: AWS Edition bootcamp - https://bootcamps.pentesteracademy.com/course/
- FLAWS AWS pentest training (CTF with hints) - http://flaws.cloud , http://flaws2.cloud
- Pentester Academy Attacking and Defending Azure AD Cloud: Beginner's Edition - https://bootcamps.pentesteracademy.com/course/

## Further Possible Trainings

- GIAC Cloud - https://www.giac.org/certification/cloud-penetration-tester-gcpn
- SANS Cloud Pentest - https://www.giac.org/certification/cloud-penetration-tester-gcpn
- Hacker Associate OCP - https://hackerassociate.com/training-and-certification/ocpt-offensive-cloud-penetration-testing/
- Infosec Cloud Bootcamp - https://www.infosecinstitute.com/courses/cloud-penetration-testing-boot-camp/
- IACert Cloud CCPT - https://www.iacertification.org/ccpt_certified_cloud_penetration_tester.html
